This is a bright, outdoor photograph of a young Black woman on a construction site.

She is the central focus, smiling as she looks down at a tablet computer she's holding with both hands. She is wearing standard safety gear: a white hard hat and an orange high-visibility vest over a grey knit top. A watch is visible on her left wrist.

The background features a large, modern building under active construction, covered in green scaffolding. A crane can be seen rising above the structure against a blue sky with scattered white clouds.

The image conveys a sense of professionalism, progress, and competence, highlighting a woman in a skilled role within the construction industry. The lighting is natural and strong, suggesting it was taken during the day.
